      </ul>
      <h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Television_version">Television version</span></h2>
      <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">In 2003, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_Broadcasting_Company" title="American Broadcasting Company">ABC</a>'s <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wonderful_World_of_Disney" title="Wonderful World of Disney">Wonderful World of Disney</a> aired a new film adaptation, reuniting two actors from the original: Kevin Hooks (who played the son) directed and Paul Winfield (who played the father) played the role of the teacher.</p>
